rows.name:
My dad was saying that Drivers
develop differently from normal people,
you know?

rows.label: tlk41200121_01_msg0002
rows.name:
He said they think about which skills to develop
based on the experience they've built up.

rows.label: tlk41200121_01_msg0003
rows.name: It's the complete opposite of normal people.

rows.label: tlk41200121_01_msg0004
rows.name:
That's why Drivers have to regularly
consider how they're going to grow from now on.
